rComments: She is one of the best language teachers I've ever had. Integrates useful exercises with the lesson and doesn't just rely on the textbook. Definitely recommended.
One of my favorite Chinese TAs by far. Very nice and good at imparting the ideas, imo.
Very friendly and willing to help. Tests are a good reflection of class, so going to class is really important! Make sure you know the dialogues really well before a test
